      "author": "o1xhack",
      "description": "Backfill modal improvements.\n\nChanges:\n- Adds quick range presets for last 7 days, last 30 days, this month, and last month.\n- Presets only fill date inputs; users still confirm with Start backfill before files are created.\n- Shows live inclusive range length and existing daily note count.\n- Disables confirmation for invalid ranges or when there are no missing daily notes to create.\n- Clamps future end dates to today and caps oversized ranges at 3650 days.\n- Adds focused unit tests for preset ranges, validation, clamping, truncation, and existing-note counting.",
