      "author": "o1xhack",
      "description": "Initial Daily Note Plus release.\n\nChanges:\n- Renames the plugin to Daily Note Plus while keeping the Obsidian plugin ID as daily-note-plus.\n- Detects existing daily notes using the configured Daily Notes/Periodic Notes folder plus the full date format.\n- Supports nested daily note formats such as YYYY/MM/DD and YYYY/YYYY.MM.DD when checking for missing notes.\n- Preserves strict parsing so notes with extra title text are not misidentified.",
